<h2>Ongoing Costs to Budget For</h2>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Hosting</strong>: Ksh 8,000–25,000/year (fast hosting is critical for e-commerce)</li>
  <li><strong>Domain renewal</strong>: Ksh 1,000–2,000/year</li>
  <li><strong>SSL certificate</strong>: Often included with hosting</li>
  <li><strong>M-Pesa transaction fees</strong>: Safaricom charges a small percentage per transaction</li>
  <li><strong>Maintenance</strong>: Ksh 3,000–8,000/month for updates, security, and support</li>
</ul>

